  • An essential addition to your wardrobe!

    Featuring an adorable frog printed on the front, this hoodie is crafted from a soft plush polyester fabric, providing you with unparalleled comfort. Available in a wide selection of colors and 4 sizes, this hoodie is a must-have for those looking for a cute twist on fashion.

    Measurements are shown below. We recommend comparing the measurements to a hoodie that fits to avoid any disappointment. If in doubt, just go one size up because a larger hoodie is always comfy to wear!

    Available in 7 different sizes for all to wear, measurements are shown below.

    Size (inches) XS S M L XL XXL XXXL

    Features

    🐸 Made from 80% premium polyester microfiber & 20% premium soft cotton
    🐸 Promotes warmth, comfort, and durability

    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.


  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning
